    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>14th-level Clockwork Soul feature</i></p><p>You gain the ability to align your consciousness to the endless calculations of Mechanus. As a bonus action, you can enter this state for 1 minute. For the duration, attack rolls against you can't benefit from advantage, and whenever you make an attack roll, an ability check, or a saving throw, you can treat a roll of 9 or lower on the [[/r d20]] as a 10.</p><p>Once you use this bonus action, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you spend 5 sorcery points to use it again.</p></div>",
